abort.invalid_webhook_url:
Home Assistant is not configured correctly to receive updates from SmartThings. The webhook URL is invalid:
> {webhook_url}

Please update your configuration per the [instructions]({component_url}), restart Home Assistant, and try again.

oauth_credentials.description:
Create a **WebHook SmartApp** in the [SmartThings Developer Portal]({developer_url}) with the following webhook URL:
> {webhook_url}

Then enter the **App ID**, **OAuth Client ID**, and **OAuth Client Secret** from the portal below.

user.description:
SmartThings will be configured to send push updates to Home Assistant at:
> {webhook_url}

If this is not correct, please update your configuration, restart Home Assistant, and try again.
